Package net.fauxpark.stringes

Class Stringe

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fauxpark.stringes.Stringe
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CharSequence, Iterable<Chare>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Token
    public class Stringe
extends Object
implements CharSequence, Iterable<Chare>
    Represents a string or a substring in relation to its parent. Provides line number, column, offset and other useful data.
